LabSampleTransportation

agents:
	robots: Nurse1, Robot1
locations: patientFloors, laboratory
resources: samples

Nurse1:
	1-5: moveTo patientFloors
	6: deliver laboratory
	7: enterData samples
	8: moveTo sampleLocation
	9: collectSample()
	10: scanBarcode(sample)
	11: moveTo lockedDrawer()
	12: openLockedDrawer()
	13: pickSample()
	14: closeLockedDrawer()

Robot1:
	1-4: moveTo laboratory
	5: receiveDelivery()
	6: scanBarcode(sample)
	7: sortSamples()
	8: loadModule()
	9: trackTime()

locked drawer:
	moveTo(laboratory, secureLockedDrawer())

scenario:
	1-3: nurses move to patient floors and collect samples
	4-6: nurses enter data into track system and move to sample location
	7-9: robots move to laboratory and receive delivery of samples
	10-12: nurses collect samples and scan barcodes
	13-15: robots sort and load samples into analysis machines
	16-18: nurses close locked drawers and track time

actions:

* moveTo: moves the agent to a specific location
* enterData: enters data into the track system
* collectSample: collects a sample
* scanBarcode: scans the barcode on a sample
* moveTolockedDrawer: moves the agent to a locked drawer in the laboratory
* openLockedDrawer: opens the locked drawer
* pickSample: picks up a sample from the locked drawer
* closeLockedDrawer: closes the locked drawer
* receiveDelivery: receives a delivery of samples from the nurses
* scanBarcode: scans the barcode on a sample
* sortSamples: sorts the samples based on their barcodes
* loadModule: loads the samples into the analysis machines
* trackTime: tracks the time between sample collection and laboratory delivery

conditions:

* presence(nurses): checks if there are any nurses in the patient floors
* presence(robots): checks if there are any robots in the laboratory
* absence(samples): checks if there are any samples in the locked drawers
* barcodeMatch(sample, barcode): checks if the barcode on a sample matches the expected barcode
* timeAccordingToProtocols: checks if the time between sample collection and laboratory delivery is within the protocol range.
